{"tid":2013893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機場報案中心警員疑私吞失物 被控盜竊明天提堂","createTime":"2020-05-12T15:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T21:33:29.000Z","uid":33709,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33f53d2e6aba8ce9b557d54b1244ac9c44a01d1c","tid":2013893,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"機場客運大樓報案中心去年發生懷疑警員監守自盜案件，事件經過一年零三個月後，26歲姓馮警員今日被控以一項「盜竊」罪，案件將於明日（13日）在沙田裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於去年2月13日，一名31歲姓楊女子在機場拾獲一個內有約5萬元現金的銀包，之後交到機場客運大樓的報案中心，由當值警務人員處理有關失物，惟1個多小時後物主到報案中心報失及認領，揭發當值警員並未立案，懷疑有人監守自盜，警方其後調查以涉嫌「盜竊」拘捕一名26歲姓馮警員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200512&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60932490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200512%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60932490&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=0d5dfa8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200512%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60932490&h=7308e38e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200512&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60932490</a><br />\n<br />\n忠誠勇毅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164c85834b740539bc3b6d5c1fd66395b03fd98f","tid":2013893,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"咁都得"},{"pid":"2544591a1e11088e44abf048f215dd2f05d8ee10","tid":2013893,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"慣常手法都要拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2bd6e8b797239c39531e399857a1c7dedd0ff8","tid":2013893,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;